    "image_with_text_wKVLmh": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_CLbqn8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With over 20 years of experience as a celebrated makeup artist and hairstylist, Marlayna is an accomplished entrepreneur, trauma-informed holistic healer, mentor, advisor, and graphic/web designer. She co-founded <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hypechocolate.co\">Hype Chocolate</a> and is the founder of both <a href=\"https://hyperelations.ca/\">Hype Relations</a> and <a href=\"https://thereikigaiamarket.com/\">The Reiki Gaia Market</a>. As a business owner and creative, she brings extensive knowledge and leadership across multiple industries, fostering a calm and positive work environment.</p><p>Marlayna's work is rooted in a commitment to systemic change, with a focus on healing communities and removing barriers for youth. Her partnership with <a href=\"https://accessfutures.com/bladerunners/\">ACCESS</a>, an organization supporting Indigenous career development, exemplifies her dedication to empowering the next generation. This extends to her involvement in mentorship programs, where she leads initiatives like the first all-Indigenous internship class at Blanche Macdonald, in collaboration with <a href=\"https://www.vifw.ca/\">Vancouver Indigenous Fashion Week</a>.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_CLbqn8"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/MARLAYNA-2019.jpg",
        "height": "adapt",
        "desktop_image_width": "medium",
        "layout": "text_first",
        "desktop_content_position": "middle",
        "desktop_content_alignment": "left",
        "content_layout": "no-overlap",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
