        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 48
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_NjQ3EM": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_ENV8fL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Outside of her professional commitments, Marlayna is an avid outdoor enthusiast and business owner, finding balance through activities like ATV riding, wakeboarding, surfing, cycling, and participating in cultural ceremonies. Her core values of inclusivity, curiosity, and progressiveness guide her work, whether as a business owner, in the beauty industry, as a mentor, or as an artist. She remains steadfast in her dedication to working with diverse communities, especially within the Indigenous community, ensuring that her work creates lasting impact and life-changing opportunities.</p><p>We spent the morning with Marlayna to hear more about the inspiration behind Hype Chocolate. Read the full interview below.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
